                     <interp inst="t18330905-188-person1776" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer; I took the prisoner with this property on him.</p>
               <p>Mr. Mitchell, a hair dresser, gave the prisoner a good character.</p>
